139
00:08:35,561 --> 00:08:37,187
- Aku sangat kecewa.
- Ayo.

140
00:08:37,688 --> 00:08:39,732
- Jangan sentuh aku!
- Sampai jumpa, Pak!

141
00:08:39,815 --> 00:08:40,899
